  <brief_title>Dynamic Laryngotracheal Separation for Aspiration</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dynamic Laryngotracheal Separation for Aspiration. Prevention of Silent Aspiration Pneumonia During Swallowing by an Implanted Stimulator</official_title>
